# Image Directory Structure
#
# Add your Instagram photos here organized as follows:
#
# portraits/
#   hero.jpg          — Main hero portrait
#   about.jpg         — About section portrait
#   about-2.jpg       — Secondary about image
#
# lifestyle/
#   01.jpg  02.jpg  03.jpg  (and more)
#
# fashion/
#   01.jpg  02.jpg  03.jpg
#
# travel/
#   01.jpg  02.jpg  03.jpg
#
# family/
#   01.jpg  02.jpg
#
# memories/
#   01.jpg  (and more)
#
# All images are automatically picked up by the site.
# WebP format is preferred for best performance.
